  "keyFeatures": [
    "VAST 4.x compliant ad parsing with full wrapper resolution",
    "Multi-platform support for WebOS, Tizen, Vidaa, and WhaleOS",
    "Nuclear Mute autoplay strategy with soft-fail recovery",
    "Remote control key normalization and focus management",
    "Comprehensive event system for ad lifecycle tracking",
    "Intelligent media file selection optimized for Smart TV hardware"
